{"tid":1868172,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消委會正聯同香港大學和科學園等機構 合作研究可自行在家製作的口罩","createTime":"2020-02-07T12:11:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T13:38:56.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"50645ea101429fb21f0fc1a50ff83e77b8196cfd","tid":1868172,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:11:44.000Z","msg":"商界立法會議員林健鋒說，正在本地籌設口罩生產線，現時已訂購首部機器，最快四星期後完成裝配投入生產，預料可每日生產十萬個。<br />\n<br />\n消息說，消委會正聯同香港大學和科學園等機構，合作研究可自行在家製作的口罩。但有傳染病醫生提醒，要留意選用物料及製作過程能否做到消毒的問題。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507290-20200207.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507290-20200207.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2FXNhycaKVB9NPWqbniWxn4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=b3b49c53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507290-20200207.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=cbde3346\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507290-20200207.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"750dc72bc62ea8627fa32d75128861419a16f6f0","tid":1868172,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:13:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"147e6977b99c8d82f34c22742f3d085026a8a83d","tid":1868172,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:13:35.000Z","msg":"2019年11月8日早上約8時，22歲的香港科技大學學生周梓樂在伊利沙伯醫院確認離世。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eRfsLS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eRfsLS</a>"},{"pid":"4db8822d816d341e9200c56f6e2423397b6dbf71","tid":1868172,"uid":271857,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:14:09.000Z","msg":"消委會快啲倡議禁淘寶劣質貨。<br />\n啲人用到病咗睇醫生又係香港人找數。"},{"pid":"ef8060457724baa9ad8f011381d432dc566f05bd","tid":1868172,"uid":273703,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTi